Deploying the MediaHub website
============================================

Prerequisites
-------------
The developer needs a SSH account on `mediahub.unl.edu` and
has to be in the `ucomm` group.


Local setup
-----------
::

$ git remote add live ssh://mediahub.unl.edu/var/www/html/mediahub.unl.edu

Deployment
----------
::

$ git push live master
